---
import Layout from '~/layouts/InquiryLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<Layout metadata={{ title: 'Compatibility Guide — Find Parts Without a Model Number', ignoreTitleTemplate: true }}>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-slate-950 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-16 lg:py-22">
      <div data-reveal class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-teal-400">Compatibility Guide</p>
        <h1 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk Variable', sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.03em;">
          Don't Know Your Model Number?
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
          You don't need one. Our interface-first matching system lets you find the right replacement part by measuring what matters — connection type, key dimensions, and electrical specs. No model number, no serial lookup, no guesswork.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Interface-First -->
  <section class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-800">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-14 lg:py-18">
      <div data-reveal class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk Variable', sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
          Why Interface Matching Works Better
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
          Traditional replacement requires a model number, but evaporative coolers often have missing labels, multiple OEM variants, or obsolete series. We match by the physical and electrical characteristics of the part itself — the parameters that actually determine whether a replacement fits and functions.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1" class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-6 dark:border-slate-800">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-teal-100 dark:bg-teal-900/30">
            <Icon name="tabler:ruler" class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Measurable</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">You can measure thread size, shaft diameter, or pad dimensions with basic tools. No special equipment needed.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2" class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-6 dark:border-slate-800">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-teal-100 dark:bg-teal-900/30">
            <Icon name="tabler:arrows-exchange" class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Universal</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">Interface types are standard across manufacturers. A 1/2" threaded pump connection is the same regardless of brand.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal data-reveal-delay="3" class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-6 dark:border-slate-800">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-teal-100 dark:bg-teal-900/30">
            <Icon name="tabler:shield-check" class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Reliable</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">If the interface, dimensions, and specs match, the part will work — regardless of what model it was originally made for.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Four Matching Methods -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800/30">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-14 lg:py-18">
      <div data-reveal class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk Variable', sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
          Four Ways to Match Your Part
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Choose the method that matches the information you have. Combine approaches for the most confident match.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <a href="/compatibility/interface" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1"
          class="group block rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-teal-300 hover:shadow-md dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-900/50 dark:hover:border-teal-700">
          <Icon name="tabler:plug" class="h-7 w-7 text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110" />
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk Variable', sans-serif;">By Interface</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">Threaded, flanged, push-fit, hose barb, or clamp mount. The connection point is the most reliable matching parameter.</p>
          <span class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-medium text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400">Browse threaded, push-fit &amp; more <Icon name="tabler:arrow-right" class="h-3 w-3"/></span>
        </a>
        <a href="/compatibility/dimensions" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2"
          class="group block rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-teal-300 hover:shadow-md dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-900/50 dark:hover:border-teal-700">
          <Icon name="tabler:ruler" class="h-7 w-7 text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110" />
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk Variable', sans-serif;">By Dimensions</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">Shaft diameter, pad size, bolt pattern, frame dimensions. Physical fit is determined by key measurements.</p>
          <span class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-medium text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400">Browse 12mm shaft, 600mm pads <Icon name="tabler:arrow-right" class="h-3 w-3"/></span>
        </a>
        <a href="/compatibility/electrical" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="3"
          class="group block rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-teal-300 hover:shadow-md dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-900/50 dark:hover:border-teal-700">
          <Icon name="tabler:chart-bar" class="h-7 w-7 text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110" />
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk Variable', sans-serif;">By Electrical</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">Voltage, power (W), RPM. Electrical components must match operating parameters for safe, correct function.</p>
          <span class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-medium text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400">Browse 110V, 220V, RPM ranges <Icon name="tabler:arrow-right" class="h-3 w-3"/></span>
        </a>
        <a href="/compatibility/cross-reference" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="4"
          class="group block rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-teal-300 hover:shadow-md dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-900/50 dark:hover:border-teal-700">
          <Icon name="tabler:books" class="h-7 w-7 text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 transition-transform group-hover:scale-110" />
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk Variable', sans-serif;">Cross-Reference</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">Find alternatives by part function — pump, seal, motor, capacitor. Follow the replacement chain.</p>
          <span class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-medium text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400">Browse functional chains <Icon name="tabler:arrow-right" class="h-3 w-3"/></span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Compatibility Evidence System -->
  <section class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-800">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-14 lg:py-18">
      <div data-reveal class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk Variable', sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
          How We Confirm Compatibility
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
          Every product listing includes compatibility evidence that tells you how confident the match is, and what parameters were used to verify it.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Evidence Types</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-100 p-4 dark:border-slate-800">
              <Icon name="tabler:plug" class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <div><p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Interface Match</p><p class="text-xs text-muted">Connection type verified — threaded, flange, push-fit, or bracket.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-100 p-4 dark:border-slate-800">
              <Icon name="tabler:ruler" class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <div><p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Dimensional Match</p><p class="text-xs text-muted">Key dimensions confirmed — shaft diameter, pad size, bolt pattern.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-100 p-4 dark:border-slate-800">
              <Icon name="tabler:bolt" class="h-5 w-5 text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
              <div><p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Electrical Match</p><p class="text-xs text-muted">Voltage, power, RPM verified — operates safely within specified range.</p></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Confidence Levels</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-green-200 bg-green-50/50 p-4 dark:border-green-800 dark:bg-green-900/10">
              <span class="flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-600 text-xs font-bold text-white flex-shrink-0">&#x2713;</span>
              <div><p class="text-sm font-medium text-green-800 dark:text-green-300">Guaranteed</p><p class="text-xs text-green-700 dark:text-green-400">Full interface, dimension, and electrical match confirmed.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50/50 p-4 dark:border-amber-800 dark:bg-amber-900/10">
              <span class="flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-amber-500 text-xs font-bold text-white flex-shrink-0">~</span>
              <div><p class="text-sm font-medium text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-300">Most Common</p><p class="text-xs text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-400">High probability — the standard replacement in most cases.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-blue-200 bg-blue-50/50 p-4 dark:border-blue-800 dark:bg-blue-900/10">
              <span class="flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-500 text-xs font-bold text-white flex-shrink-0">?</span>
              <div><p class="text-sm font-medium text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-300">Needs Confirmation</p><p class="text-xs text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400">Contact us with photos or measurements for final verification.</p></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How to Identify Your Part -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800/30 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-slate-800">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-14 lg:py-18">
      <div data-reveal class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk Variable', sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
          Step-by-Step: How to Identify Your Part
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">A systematic approach. Complete these steps and you'll have everything needed to find the right replacement.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 max-w-4xl">
        <div data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
          <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-600/25 dark:text-teal-400/20" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk Variable', sans-serif;">01</span>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Determine the System</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">Which part of the cooler? Water system, evaporation, air movement, electrical, structure, or maintenance.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2">
          <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-600/25 dark:text-teal-400/20" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk Variable', sans-serif;">02</span>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Check the Interface</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">How does it connect? Threaded, flanged, push-fit, or clamped. Measure thread diameter or bolt pattern.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal data-reveal-delay="3">
          <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-600/25 dark:text-teal-400/20" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk Variable', sans-serif;">03</span>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Measure Key Dimensions</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">Shaft diameter, pad size, bolt hole spacing. Use calipers or a ruler — millimeters are best.</p>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal data-reveal-delay="4">
          <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-600/25 dark:text-teal-400/20" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk Variable', sans-serif;">04</span>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Note Electrical Specs</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">Voltage, power (W), RPM. Check the label on your existing motor or pump for these values.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div data-reveal class="mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
        <a href="/how-to-identify-part-number" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-teal-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-teal-500">
          Full Identification Guide <Icon name="tabler:arrow-right" class="h-4 w-4"/>
        </a>
        <a href="/inquiry" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 transition-colors hover:bg-gray-50 dark:border-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-800 dark:text-gray-300 dark:hover:bg-slate-700">
          <Icon name="tabler:mail" class="h-4 w-4"/> Not Sure? Send Us a Photo
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-slate-950 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 text-center lg:py-20">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk Variable', sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
        Have Measurements Ready?
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base text-gray-400 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Include your interface type, dimensions, and electrical specs in your inquiry. Our team will confirm compatibility and provide a quote within 24 hours.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
        <a href="/inquiry" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-teal-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-teal-500">
          <Icon name="tabler:mail" class="h-4 w-4"/> Request a Quote
        </a>
        <a href="/compatibility/interface" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-white/15 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-white/5">
          Start Matching by Interface <Icon name="tabler:arrow-right" class="h-4 w-4"/>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
